{"tid":1252202,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點解香港攪唔成大規模罷工？","createTime":"2019-06-23T01:14:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T07:22:22.000Z","uid":261166,"like":71,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"9986d8f83c217670bdc57ecb2d2c299eec38e0ca","tid":1252202,"uid":261166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T01:14:37.000Z","msg":"罷工係不合作運動重要一環，大家集思廣益！請進言！"},{"pid":"46215dcd19288aaff85bcb0ea7bda0c422cec1d7","tid":1252202,"uid":265467,"like":9,"dislike":13,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T01:15:45.000Z","msg":"Sorry ，借位一用<br />\n<br />\n大家應該由問題根源去思考，與其一樣樣去反對政府D賣港政策，點解唔用真普選趕走曬班賣港賊，必須要令更多人知問題根源核心，個個支持真普選！！！<br />\n<br />\n現有大家要爭取D問題層次如果向上推，就會發現係香港現有制度出現問題，一日冇真普選，相同問題絕對會源源不絕！！！<br />\n<br />\n一日無真普選,建制派，港共政權賣港賊一車車補上，要徹底趕走賣港賊,只有真普選！！！各自跑山，真香港人加油！！<br />\n<br />\n［真普選救祖國行動］200年前香港割讓救國，如今中共有難，香港再割責無旁貸！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1252184\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1252184</a><br />\n<br />\n［請廣傳］香港只有真普選先可以趕走港共政府同建制派賣港賊！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1251736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1251736</a>"},{"pid":"724bf28604dfc27b26bbcb3b16e8308ebff20c01","tid":1252202,"uid":61853,"like":86,"dislike":1,"score":85,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T01:19:48.000Z","msg":"冇公會領導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edece1b9aa1fadb3100aef55f6c431c5a31654fe","tid":1252202,"uid":40470,"like":16,"dislike":34,"score":-18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T01:22:20.000Z","msg":"樓主你d死廢撚返工得萬零蚊就無所謂姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b31d95e817151c5eda6ad09e0370c84322bc2c3e","tid":1252202,"uid":261166,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"quote":{"pid":"724bf28604dfc27b26bbcb3b16e8308ebff20c01","tid":1252202,"uid":61853,"like":86,"dislike":1,"score":85,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T01:19:48.000Z","msg":"冇公會領導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 