應係理所當然，所以<br />\n一係就等<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">現有工會爭取更完善法律保障</span></span>，才能以罷工作為不合作運動的手段；<br />\n一係就行使基本法權利，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">工人另組工會</span></span>，以新工會團結工人，直接面對資方<br />\n<br />\n講黎講去，都係要先有工會保障，才可以考慮罷工！"},{"pid":"2abc1e0690dd3f7211248d73d0bf26c99d659292","tid":1252202,"uid":231291,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T01:28:10.000Z","msg":"因為出得黎既絕大部份都係比政治玩既青年，你問大中學既青年罷工？<span style=\"color: red;\">佢地都無返工！</span><br />\n<br />\n至於懂得政治是什麼既工作人士，根本清楚今次只是政治騷，你行出黎就比議員玩，更何況罷工？為左政治演員既十萬人工你賠上自己份工？傻的嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12778c5af94ad6e04aab42c6daa0b9f52cb4c854","tid":1252202,"uid":261166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e2b17db2b1b2bacc96c5c8a194318ab55a8269f","tid":1252202,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T12:34:53.000Z","msg":"因為冇工會啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過連登仔咁右又點會支持工運 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T01:33:03.000Z","msg":"不如試下，攪返「<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">工連會</span></span>」，We Connect <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f06f15a26ae336d88f07223d6bc08831d22e077b","tid":1252202,"uid":267221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9986d8f83c217670bdc57ecb2d2c299eec38e0ca","tid":1252202,"uid":261166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T01:14:37.000Z","msg":"罷工係不合作運動重要一環，大家集思廣益！請進言！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T01:39:49.000Z","msg":"香港係資本主義商業城市<br />\n政府一向政策都偏重商家利益同地產霸權<br />\n商家佬又點會比啲人成立工會去倒自己米<br />\n可以試下去問下啲HR<br />\n你話搞過工會睇佢地仲會唔會請<br />\n所以冇工會就冇人帶頭<br />\n冇件帶頭就會人人自危驚秋後算帳<br />\n香港幾多中產打工仔又要供樓又要養細路<br />\n你叫佢禮拜出來遊行抗爭或者都冇問題<br />\n但罷工 佢地跟本冇呢個本錢"},{"pid":"83d1013591500b5f48772411348e95ec8f9e5103","tid":1252202,"uid":237300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c6b90f21a5419dd9315a84b7fdb82366bc6a663","tid":1252202,"uid":7766,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T01:42:09.000Z","msg":"無集體談判權"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T01:44:16.000Z","msg":"呢個要多謝工聯會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5847b2d0e18ee6fcf7c106d8138f667ba246b0eb","tid":1252202,"uid":237300,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c5ccca6807dc2d1bc847236c2822d47137aa3cc9","tid":1252202,"uid":261166,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"2c9a0848b418e41938c517f7f6426d6dc40ac9a9","tid":1252202,"uid":55745,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T02:24:03.000Z","msg":"因為啲人跟本唔想付出"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T02:53:30.000Z","msg":"香港最唔缺 Smart guy , 唔係唔想付出，係要講風險同回報 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果個個都知成部門有一半以上人唔返工，返果個咪會覺得自己好笨7 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T01:46:42.000Z","msg":"儍啦，返嗰個可能覺得上位機會嚟啦，人棄我取，奶鞋底ready"},{"pid":"e053481a38a5855a788638775cc4eb7fe053fdc6","tid":1252202,"uid":261166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2abc1e0690dd3f7211248d73d0bf26c99d659292","tid":1252202,"uid":231291,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T01:28:10.000Z","msg":"因為出得黎既絕大部份都係比政治玩既青年，你問大中學既青年罷工？<span style=\"color: red;\">佢地都無返工！</span><br />\n<br />\n至於懂得政治是什麼既工作人士，根本清楚今次只是政治騷，你行出黎就比議員玩，更何況罷工？為左政治演員既十萬人工你賠上自己份工？傻的嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T01:50:06.000Z","msg":"呢幾年，政府同政棍玩遊戲規則玩得太出神入化， DQ、選區劃分、配票、拉布...等，另議會代議失效，結果議題每每要帶上街，變相公投，增加成本，減低效率。<br />\n<br />\n罷工都唔係理想做法，我同普通打工仔一樣，如果老細們諗清諗楚傾掂左，咁細嘅咪做囉，好過吓吓無方向，就叫細嘅死掂佢，罷工之後 d 野咪又要跟返，真係好得閒咩，但多一張牌點都好過無得出，用唔用一件事，依家問題係罷工唔係一張可以用的牌，要諗辦法增加大家籌碼。"},{"pid":"1aa4eb110b5e65e7786e9c88b1d0555bdef4d401","tid":1252202,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T01:54:41.000Z","msg":"Money is death of duty"},{"pid":"8ac3e848374f7d71d10ecaae347836baaff640d0","tid":1252202,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T01:57:22.000Z","msg":"外國公會係個個月扣錢比會費, 一講收錢自然搞唔成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee07b9659bb08182695173625f788a1d1931ffff","tid":1252202,"uid":168368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b31d95e817151c5eda6ad09e0370c84322bc2c3e","tid":1252202,"uid":261166,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"quote":{"pid":"724bf28604dfc27b26bbcb3b16e8308ebff20c01","tid":1252202,"uid":61853,"like":86,"dislike":1,"score":85,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T01:19:48.000Z","msg":"冇公會領導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T01:28:25.000Z","msg":"認同，就算香港部分行業有工會，但以我所知背景二元，唔係親建就反建，好少人參加。<br />\n<br />\n我提議從下而上建立中間派工會團結大多數，為日後運動增加能量！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T02:21:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ccd3209ee0d94aaa5a4e89fd6e931ac15317bce","tid":1252202,"uid":168368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T02:47:04.000Z","msg":"聽你地咁講  睇黎狗建制 垃圾正苦好耐以前就下了一場好大既棋  教練 球証 足協都係佢地既人<br />\n令到啲人唔罷工  極邪惡"},{"pid":"3aea991f3ec13d30ef28863ab16f8a7210feef0e","tid":1252202,"uid":153570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T02:49:47.000Z","msg":"體制既極致"},{"pid":"8ed700b6c184ea34cd0960734fd70dc9ca9ddbbc","tid":1252202,"uid":36324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09435ab441c4666d2c1a1529b1c3515a552c868f","tid":1252202,"uid":261166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aca41336ea7b6270c022dc38fffa6323c7e1961a","tid":1252202,"uid":264626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T15:59:10.000Z","msg":"柏林圍牆倒下，蘇聯解體，其中一個共通點係人民生活困苦，窮，如果抗爭，個 cost 未必好大，但香港失業率低，大家有份工，生活過得去，罷工成本相對高，搞唔起。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T01:20:34.000Z","msg":"成本主要來自以下：<br />\n收入減少：如手停口停、佣金減少、meet 唔到 target 影響 performance ......<br />\n裁員風險：秋後算帳、寫花CV ......<br />\n<br />\n既然以上成本咁高/風險咁大，罷工得唔到響應係理所當然，所以<br />\n一係就等<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">現有工會爭取更完善法律保障</span></span>，才能以罷工作為不合作運動的手段；<br />\n一係就行使基本法權利，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">工人另組工會</span></span>，以新工會團結工人，直接面對資方<br />\n<br />\n講黎講去，都係要先有工會保障，才可以考慮罷工！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T02:53:59.000Z","msg":"兩樣都有問題<br />\n<br />\n第一樣：冇行政立法控制權，好難做到<br />\n<br />\n第二樣：你整個新工會出嚟咪一樣面對同一堆法律，同一個政治經濟格局 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e7779ce57df9c14be20406fa55d387b66d6c740","tid":1252202,"uid":230146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T02:56:11.000Z","msg":"我地d工會冇權冇財力，<br />\n立法會佔既議席少，<br />\n而且人地罷工，<br />\n工會係有錢俾，<br />\n香港要倒貼，分分鐘秋後算帳；<br />\n中低下階層個個月都係搵得岩岩夠洗，<br />\n承受唔到呢個風險"},{"pid":"4a778200736e20dbace50ce0e7a291f901336159","tid":1252202,"uid":261166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ac3e848374f7d71d10ecaae347836baaff640d0","tid":1252202,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T01:57:22.000Z","msg":"外國公會係個個月扣錢比會費, 一講收錢自然搞唔成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T03:03:57.000Z","msg":"世事都被你看透了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb0a01641f952b7efa46e7d1ad61b62bd0775a44","tid":1252202,"uid":34140,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a0e9a1efa12705d